Here's the PlantUML sequence diagram for the `Nishu0_anime_nft_marketplace` focusing on the control flow during NFT purchase:

```plantuml
@startuml Nishu0_anime_nft_marketplace

actor User
participant "Frontend (Next.js)" as Frontend
participant "NFTContext" as Context
participant "Smart Contract" as Contract
participant "Wallet (MetaMask)" as Wallet
participant "IPFS" as IPFS

User -> Frontend: Clicks "Buy NFT"
Frontend -> Context: buyNft(nftId, price)
Context -> Wallet: Request transaction signing
Wallet --> User: Shows transaction confirmation
User -> Wallet: Confirms transaction
Wallet -> Contract: execute buyNFT(nftId, price)
Contract -> Contract: Validate ownership\nTransfer NFT\nUpdate balances
Contract --> Wallet: Transaction receipt
Wallet --> Context: Transaction confirmation
Context -> IPFS: Fetch NFT metadata
IPFS --> Context: NFT metadata
Context --> Frontend: Update UI (NFT ownership)
Frontend --> User: Show success message

@enduml
```